title: What Can Happen in a Year?
itunes:title: What Can Happen in a Year?
description:
Episode 612 - We live in a world of instant gratification. The problem with that is that most people want success now, they don't want to wait for it. But greatness, success, and an amazing life take time. In this episode, I am going to teach you how to play the long game in life. You might not get what you want right now, but you will definitely get what you want soon. Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
